Sandman Presents - Lucifer, The Morningstar Option

Vertigo, 1999

Written by Mike Carey

Illustrated by Scott Hampton

In which Lucifer (having retired from Hell to run his jazz club Lux) is approached by an angel who requests that he perform a service for heaven, one which the angels themselves cannot do, and for which he will be handsomely paid
